event.title: Localgroup meeting of the FSFE Community Bonn in Bonn, Germany

body.p: On Monday 13 September, at 7pm (CEST), the monthly meeting of the Bonn FSFE Fellowship will take place. The Bonn FSFE Community Meetings ("Fellowship Meetings") take place at 7pm on the second Monday of each month. The current meeting place is Dotty's at BTHV, Christian-Miesen-Stra√üe 1, 53129 Bonn. The meetings are open to all who are interested in Free Software. This time Johannes will report about GNURadio.
